Package model.Bean

Class VisitTimetableBean

java.lang.Object
model.Bean.VisitTimetableBean
public class VisitTimetableBean
extends java.lang.Object
Author:
Tamburello Martina This class represents a visiting timetable object. It is used to define the times available for patient bookings.
